8. Clean the out directory 
  $ make clobber / make clean

9. Choose desired binary file of divice
  $ source build/envsetup.sh
  $ lunch aosp_arm-eng

10. Make everything with make command
  $ make -j4(prossesor number)

11. Finally run emulator with source
  $ emulator 
   
 
